review_text: This park needs work. It does the job but does not have much appeal to it and the structures are falling apart.

(Translated by Google) The children's facilities are old and in need of a change. The benches also. It's a shame since it is one of the rare parks where there is so much shade.

(Original)
Les installations pour enfants sont vielles et auraient besoin de changement. Les bancs également. C'est dommage puisqu'il s'agit un des rare parc où on y trouve autant d'ombre.

(Translated by Google) Empty but pretty
If it was lively it would be better

(Original)
Vide mais jolie
Si c'était animé, ce serait mieux

(Translated by Google) Too often there are sand wasps and it is unpleasant for our children to play around with insects. Otherwise the park is okay.

(Original)
Il y a trop souvent des guêpes de sables et c'est déplaisant pour nos enfants de jouer entourer de ses insectes. Sinon le parc est correct.

(Translated by Google) Very nice park, well maintained. Several benches for parents to watch children explore.
